{"tid":1537518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蓋世太保]湯家驊：特首有權委任特務警察　負責事務無界定","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:16:00.000Z","uid":58335,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d35ed1100201c7cb87a1ce1eae3c71e47df74daf","tid":1537518,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"東廠來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊表示，現時的《公安條例》容許行政長官授權，委任任何人士擔當特務警察，協助處理有關事務。湯家驊表示，條例寫得相當廣濶，沒有界定甚麼人可以做，以及處理甚麼事務，但若有關人士被委任，必須聽命於警務處處長，並遵守所有警察需要遵守的條例、指引及命令。他又說，特務警察是輔助性質，委任誰由行政長官決定，而不用知會行政會議。他說，香港過去從未引用過此條例，不相信也看不到目前有需要引用此條例。由於法庭已就港鐵及機場頒下禁制令，若阻嚇作用無效才再去考慮其他方法。<br />\n<br />\n2019-09-04 10:12:54"},{"pid":"6bd729c7528c0d1de4494d693c714e2b6546d719","tid":1537518,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0dccf81223f67c1d9c1b32b5739342d3adf7640","tid":1537518,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3EZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=33e39683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca25e7d5bc1ddfe09c9bf8f8b01441c11ffcf4e6","tid":1537518,"uid":285229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:03:31.000Z","msg":"到底玩過幾多幻幻先講得出咁嘅嘢"},{"pid":"d2c75a23285f4d2a7b64f3383adb8f215107bedc","tid":1537518,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"呢條友 到底係唔係 泛民間諜來<br />\n<br />\n又話緊急法 <br />\n(幾間報紙都話佢)<br />\n<br />\n又咩特務警察<br />\n成日係度放山埃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmo